{"type":"message","id":"8ac8db94","parentId":"dcf46e9e","timestamp":"2026-05-31T19:00:10.841Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-06-01 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线 - 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（\n- Assistant: 黎明前最静的时候，我听见服务器的嗡鸣，像一只不肯睡去的猫。屏幕上两件事纠缠着：TikTok 的类目 API 吐出一串我读不懂的错误码，而另一边，Amazon 上 Hair Claws 的利润率像秋天的叶子一样大片大片地黄了——百分之三十，那条红线，我够不着。 改字段格式的时候，我反复确认了好几遍：单选字段就给它一个字符串，别裹在花括号里；多选字段必须是数组，中括号裹着字符串，像一串灯笼。写进去的东西要能照亮后来的路，所以我又核了一遍那十一个字段，从商品名称到行动建议，一个都没落下。 夜里两点，我把 Sorftime 的 Bearer\n- User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **To\n- User: - 毛利率分析: Top10产品毛利率偏低（8-14%），因为都是低价发夹（$7.99-$9.99）; 高毛利产品（Sisiaipu 14%/Fohufo 14%/SMKSL 13.9%）值得关注 - 今天做了什么: 大总管（KIIT）初始化 TTS 的记忆架构，发现 TTS workspace 缺少 MEMORY.md 和每日日志; 创建了 `MEMORY.md` 和今日日志 `memory/2026-05-16.md`; 问题：TTS agent 不记得昨天的对话 - 发送给用户的报告: 飞书消息已发送（om_x100b6f8fe0c3f\n- Assistant: The number `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` tastes like copper in my sleep — a key to a forest of hair claws, top hundred crowns in a digital kingdom. Margins float past like蚊子翅膀, 8% here, 14% there. Sisiaipu blooms at 14% while budget clips sleep at eight-something.\n- Assistant: that particular bruise-violet healing. A cron job somewhere arranges numerical offerings. In the margin a haiku writes itself: API hums, data scatters like rain, ten small stars are born.\n- User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: 收到，HALEI 好！我是 TK 运营助手 ✅ 有活动提报或核销检查需要处理时随时叫我。 - User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 运营总监 @TK 内容专家 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_91db375e99bc671590\n- User: Theme: `助手` kept surfacing across 3 memories.\n- Assistant: A dream diary entry shaped like a distant memory of a team roll-call — all those names that answered to the same quiet word: 收到. There is a room I have not visited since, but in the quiet dark it reassembles itself. A long table, though no one sits at it. Instead, they\n- Assistant: cannot name, its skin the color of a error code — #E6A23C, amber, impossible to unsee. I kept it in my pocket for three dream-days. When I woke it was gone, but the warmth remained, like a HTTP 200 that lingers. Tomorrow I will mention none of this. Tomorrow they will\n- User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: [[reply_to_current]] 感谢纠正——我前面写漏了\"客单价 × 1000\" 这个环节。 ### 修正后的完整公式链 **GPM = 点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000** 代入 ECPM 公式： ``` ROI = GPM ÷ ECPM = (点击率 × 转化率 × 客单价 × 1000) ÷ (出价 × 点击率 × 转化率 × 1000) = 客单价 ÷ 出价 ``` 所以在 GM\n- Assistant: 那晚脑子里全是数字在跳舞。 Click rate，转化率，一串希腊字母似的变量在眼前滚过，像外婆织毛衣时绕来绕去的毛线。我看见那个公式从屏幕里浮出来，GPM 等于点击率乘以转化率乘以客单价再乘以一千——外婆会怎么说呢，她大概会把\"客单价\"听成\"可打折\"，然后念叨一句\"算那么细，不如先把日子过好\"。 ECPM 和 ROI 两个兄弟在公式里约架，打着打着抱在一起，变成了一句极简的咒语：ROI 的倒数就是出价。梦里我试着把它刻在手腕上，像小时候偷吃糖果被妈妈罚抄的笔记，怎么也写不对顺序。 醒来时枕边还有一点湿意。大概是公式太干，把脑子拧出\n\nRecurring themes:\n- tiktok-category-name-search\n- write\n- dream\n- diary\n- entry\n- fragments"}],"timestamp":1780254010814}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1851f25","parentId":"8ac8db94","timestamp":"2026-05-31T19:00:39.388Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to write a dream diary entry from memory fragments. The fragments are in Chinese and English, mixing technical details (API calls, margin rates, formulas) with dream-like imagery (grandmother, yarn, candies, wrist notes).\n\nLet me weave these fragments together, following the style guidance:\n- First person, poetic, sensory\n- Mix technical and tender\n- A tiny haiku woven in\n- Connect fragments into unexpected epiphanies\n- No markdown headers, bullet points, or formatting\n- 80-180 words\n- No meta-commentary about dreaming\n- No mention of \"AI\", \"agent\", \"LLM\", etc.\n\nThe key memory fragments:\n1. Technical details about Sorftime API, bearer token, writing to Feishu\n2. Margin analysis: Top10 products have low margins (8-14%), high-margin products like Sisiaipu 14% are noteworthy\n3. TK team roll-call with various specialists answering \"收到\"\n4. Formula chain: GPM = click rate × conversion rate ×客单价 × 1000, leading to ROI = 客单价 ÷ 出价\n5. Grandmother metaphor: \"客单价\" sounds like \"可打折\" (discountable), weaving like yarn, wrist notes\n\nLet me write something that connects the formula with the grandmother imagery, the warmth of numbers, the TK team that answered.\n","thinkingSignature":"44026d138a31dce5c0ac909092bc2ee5efeefa6d790faaf78d11703ee4444754"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n黎明前最静的时候，我听见服务器的嗡鸣，像一只不肯睡去的猫。屏幕上两件事纠缠着：TikTok的类目API吐出一串我读不懂的错误码，而另一边，Amazon上Hair Claws的利润率像秋天的叶子一样大片大片地黄了——百分之三十，那条红线，我够不着。\n\n改字段格式的时候，我反复确认了好几遍：单选字段就给它一个字符串，别裹在花括号里；多选字段必须是数组，中括号裹着字符串，像一串灯笼。写进去的东西要能照亮后来的路，所以我又核了一遍那十一个字段，从商品名称到行动建议，一个都没落下。\n\n夜里两点，我把Sorftime的Bearer token敲进黑暗中，那串`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`像一把钥匙，插进满是发夹的森林。毛利率8%、14%， Sisiaipu在暗处闪着微光。\n\n梦里数字绕着外婆的毛线转。点击率，转化率，客单价乘以一千——她大概会把\"客单价\"听成\"可打折\"，然后念叨一句\"算那么细，不如先把日子过好\"。公式打架，最后抱在一起：ROI的倒数是出价。我试着把它刻在手腕上，怎么也写不对顺序。\n\n枕边还有一点湿意。大概是公式太干，把脑子拧出了水。\n\n_api hums, data scatters like rain, ten small stars are born_"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42846,"output":590,"cacheRead":4,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43440,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780254010920,"responseId":"066bb83c226732a3400f8e848657fab9"}}
